 "Title":"Provides that municipal broadband service companies are authorized to provide broadband service to tenants in multi-family housing",
 "Summary":"Provides that municipal broadband service companies are authorized to provide broadband service to tenants in multi-family housing; provides that landlords shall not interfere with the installation of such service, demand or accept payment for allowing the service on the property, or discriminate in rental charges between tenants who receive broadband service and those that don't.",
